Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我存在於此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊呢？ 還是你們那邊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也曾存在於你們那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.57,0:00:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這兒和那兒是連繫著的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然如此 但真正的我到底在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許真正的我是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只存在那些認識我的人心內
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在跟你們傾談的我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Layer:13 EGO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉體不是沒有意義的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了你所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是出錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩這麼多菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在減肥嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 這些事不要說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒有人要送貨來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貨送來後 先替我付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是電腦配件?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲 我們今晚去不去玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CYBERIA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要發E-MAIL了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲 你要發給誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會又是她吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千砂同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 四方田千砂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你叫我們帶她到CYBERIA去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千砂跟那裡格格不入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫她也不會再去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 只是突然想到一些怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些怪事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶中沒有的事就是不存在的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記億？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶中沒有那個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那人就根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲 你在說誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說那個人不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點下課就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 我又輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來真是個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這些很有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 快點嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽在等我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那麼拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再猜一次 再猜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎不等你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡滑了 再猜一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要辭職了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要離開這個公司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們竟要我做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要辭職 一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要辭職 絕對要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶中沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就根本沒發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶只是一種記錄\N把它整理一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為所有人的記憶都沒有你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這不是你所希望的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再有人離奇的死去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再有人受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會被人所憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網絡上會令人死亡的訊息已經全部消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會再有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此 玲音也不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你最希望的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那個人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從來就不存在過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有也不可能變成神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要再胡思亂想了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已不存於任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不存在於任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我是誰？ 人到底在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己不是說過了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實網絡世界並存在現實世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網絡只是個傳送資料的媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料是不會停留的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它只是不斷地傳送和交換罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個人的記憶或是歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不知不覺中成為大家所共有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼龐大的記憶系統
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為人類能自行建構嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的只是連接網絡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底連接著什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類有知道那個必要麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網絡聯繫何處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不知道也能繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的世界出著各種各樣的神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類認為這樣才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡這樣的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡也沒辦法 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該明白我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 玲音根本不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音存在於任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音只能看著一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 其實玲音就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為神後會很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信會比一般人更快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事也不用管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看著就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不會有人恨玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不會有人討厭玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再從頭開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又不是沒試過重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音你到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…到底在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用再穿這件衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我…大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜錯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 下次我給你弄好喝的紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 不要再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道一定會很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實記憶…不只是過去的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它也關係到今天 甚至明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就依照你剛才所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你的心意去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但睡房的窗簾由我決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的老師 你說什麼就什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這才是個好學生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見過你嗎？ 有見過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是我實習時教過的學生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又不像 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是初次見面…的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？ 原來是初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個普通的名字對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定將來還會再見的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 說不定會再見的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠和你在一起 永遠…
